(32, 'woopay-beta-existingmerchants-noaction-27APR23', 'info', 'en_US', 'WooPay is back!', 'Thanks for previously trying WooPay, the express checkout feature built into WooCommerce Payments. Were excited to announce that WooPay availability has resumed. No action is required on your part.\r\n<br /><br />\r\nYou can now continue boosting conversions by offering your customers a simple, secure way to pay with a single click.', '{}', 'pending', 'woocommerce.com', '2025-02-14 04:48:51', NULL, 0, 'plain', '', 0, 0, 'info'),
